{"tid":2053691,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"國安法之下，公職人員在97年之前累積的退休金應該一筆勾銷","createTime":"2020-06-06T13:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T13:53:42.000Z","uid":48040,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"605f612f7c3d5b78846b2a4f88414a9b3cc393c2","tid":2053691,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:19:39.000Z","msg":"97年之前累積的退休金（年資），應該視為外國勢力提供的金錢利益。<br />\n<br />\n特別係林鄭月娥，以及警察。法官都係。應該取消他們97年之前累積的退休金，以免他們被外國勢力收買。<br />\n<br />\n回歸前的公務員享受長俸，呢d係英國收買人心的措施。現在應該立即停止支付，並且追討97年至今已經發放的長俸，並且要調查，這些港英時期的公務員，在回歸之後有否出賣祖國利益。<br />\n<br />\n公職人員有咩理由收受港英殖民地政府的利益？好有利益衝突嫌疑，不利國家安全，同收受國外勢力資助冇分別。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n------<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4nzUThz8BvI&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdxxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=43376aa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI</a>"},{"pid":"6fb233ccc956d391385bcf74135e299d76b53f3d","tid":2053691,"uid":157532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76bccd30988b309f0c89afac57b1e8f407fcb1cd","tid":2053691,"uid":281899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n鬥紅係出路"},{"pid":"84e793f475df45ec17e596a236f7960f5b647cd0","tid":2053691,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"港英殖民地政府=英國=外國勢力<br />\n港英時期的退休金=外國勢力的黑金"},{"pid":"3d279c14a4c1e440c927d7767e43a66bd81ed069","tid":2053691,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:36:34.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推 必有迴響"},{"pid":"48d313415a706f65c7874b6fb72a90959b9bd634","tid":2053691,"uid":12586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:38:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}